Please see documentation for details.

You need OpenCV 2.4.x, GPhoto 2.5.x including development packages and also QT4 SDK (4.8) packages. 

To compile it, use QT Creator and open the project file or on command line

just simply execute

make

=====

To install the dependencies on Ubuntu / Debian / Mint run:

sudo apt-get install qtcreator ocl-icd-libopencl1 \
    libopencv-dev libgphoto2-6-dev qt-sdk

The package ocl-icd-libopencl1 is added due to a packaging bug: https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/opencv/+bug/1245260
